      "parameters": {
        "content": "## [Utility] Record Rating v1.0.0\n\nWrite-back utility — records a lead's rating after they click a review link.\n\n**Inputs:** source_type ('sheet' | 'crm'), source_ref (row_number for sheet), lead_sheet_id, lead_sheet_tab, fields (object of column→value, e.g. { 'Rating Received': 'good', 'Needs Followup': true })\n\nRoutes by source_type:\n- sheet → [Utility] Update Lead Sheet Row\n- crm → throws 'not yet implemented' (seam for future CRM integration)\n\nCalled by [Reviews] Handle Rating Click after verifying the signed token.",
        "height": 260,
        "width": 560
      },
      "id": "sticky1",
      "name": "Sticky Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
